# Common Commands

Invoke with: *"how do I build"*, *"run locally"*, *"deploy"*, *"docker"*, *"what commands"*, *"npm scripts"*

Reference for all development, build, test, and deployment commands.

---

## 1. Development

### Start Full Dev Environment
```bash
npm install              # Install all workspaces
npm run dev              # Concurrently: server (8080) + client Vite (5173)
```

### Start Individual Packages
```bash
npm run dev:server       # Server only (ts-node, port 8080)
npm run dev:client       # Client only (Vite, port 5173, proxies /api → 8080)
```

### Run Poller Manually
```bash
npm run poll             # Run one poll cycle (built)
npm run dev:poll -w packages/server  # Run with ts-node
```

### Environment Variables (required for dev)
```bash
export REPORTPORTAL_URL=https://reportportal-cnv.apps...
export REPORTPORTAL_TOKEN=your-token-here

# Optional
export SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL=https://hooks.slack.com/services/...
export JIRA_URL=https://issues.redhat.com
export JIRA_TOKEN=your-jira-token
```

### Prerequisites
- Node.js >= 20
- npm (with workspaces support)
- Docker/Podman (for container builds)

---

## 2. Building

### Full Build (ordered: shared → server → client)
```bash
npm run build
```

### Individual Packages
```bash
npm run build:shared     # TypeScript → dist/ for shared
npm run build:server     # TypeScript → dist/ for server
npm run build:client     # tsc + Vite → dist/ for client
```

---

## 3. Code Quality

### Linting
```bash
npm run lint             # ESLint (--max-warnings 0)
npm run lint:fix         # ESLint autofix
```

### Formatting
```bash
npm run format           # Prettier write
npm run format:check     # Prettier check (CI)
```

### Unused Code Detection
```bash
npm run knip             # Find unused files, deps, exports
```

### Type Checking
```bash
npm run typecheck        # Typecheck shared + server
```

### Before Commit (automated via Husky)
Husky pre-commit hook runs automatically:
1. `lint-staged` -- ESLint fix + Prettier on staged files
2. `format:check` -- Prettier check on all files
3. `knip` -- Unused code detection

### Manual Full Check
```bash
npm run lint && npm run format:check && npm run knip && npm run typecheck && npm run test
```

---

## 4. Testing

### Server Tests (Vitest)
```bash
npm run test                                  # Run all (vitest run)
npm run test:watch -w packages/server         # Watch mode
npx vitest run path/to/file.test.ts -w packages/server  # Specific file
```

---

## 5. Docker

```bash
# Build image (multi-stage monorepo)
podman build -t quay.io/openshift-cnv/cnv-ui-monitor:latest .

# Run locally
podman run -it --rm \
  -p 8080:8080 \
  -e REPORTPORTAL_URL=... \
  -e REPORTPORTAL_TOKEN=... \
  -v ./data:/data \
  quay.io/openshift-cnv/cnv-ui-monitor:latest

# Push to registry
podman push quay.io/openshift-cnv/cnv-ui-monitor:latest
```

---

## 6. Kubernetes Deployment

```bash
kubectl apply -f k8s/ -n cnv-monitor
```

### Verify
```bash
kubectl get pods -n cnv-monitor
kubectl logs -f deployment/cnv-ui-monitor -n cnv-monitor
kubectl get cronjob -n cnv-monitor
```

### Trigger Manual Poll
```bash
kubectl create job --from=cronjob/cnv-ui-monitor-poll manual-poll -n cnv-monitor
kubectl logs job/manual-poll -n cnv-monitor --follow
```

