## 8. CI (GitHub Actions)

CI runs on push/PR to main:
1. `npm ci`
2. Build shared
3. Typecheck server
4. Build server
5. Test server (vitest)
6. Build client
7. Build + push Docker image (main branch only)

---

## 9. Troubleshooting

| Issue | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| `MODULE_NOT_FOUND` | `npm install` at root |
| shared types missing | `npm run build:shared` first |
| Vite proxy 502 | Start server first: `npm run dev:server` |
| SQLite errors | Check `DB_PATH` directory exists |
| RP API 401 | Check `REPORTPORTAL_TOKEN` |

### Clean Reinstall
```bash
rm -rf node_modules packages/*/node_modules packages/*/dist
npm install
npm run build
```

